<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="map" style="width:500px;height:400px;"></div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="//dapi.kakao.com/v2/maps/sdk.js?appkey=<%= MAP_KEY %>"></script>
    <script>
        var container = document.getElementById('map'); 
        var options = { 
            center: new kakao.maps.LatLng(<%= x %>, <%= y %>), 
            level: 3 
        };
        var map = new kakao.maps.Map(container, options);
    </script>

<!-- {
        fcstDate: '20230715',
        fcstTime: '0300',
        TMP: '24',
        POP: '30',
        PCP: '강수없음'
    } -->

    <% if (weather) {  %>
    <% if (weather == 'DateOverError') {  %>
        <p>3일 이내의 날씨만 알림이 가능합니다.</p>
    <% } else if (weather == 'ApiError') { %>
        <p>날씨정보를 받아오는 데에 오류가 발생하였습니다.</p>
    <% } else { %>
    <p>선택지역의</p>
    <p>날짜:<%= weather.fcstDate %> </p>
    <p>시간:<%= weather.fcstTime %> </p>
    <p>기온:<%= weather.TMP %> °C</p>
    <p>강수확률:<%= weather.POP %> %</p>
    <p>강수량:<%= weather.PCP %> </p>
    <% } %>
    <% } %>

    <p><%= stadiumResult[0].name %></p>
    <div>
        <form action="/upload" method="POST">
            <p>날짜</p>
            <input type="text" name="day" placeholder="20230811" ><br>
            <p>시간</p>
            <input type="text" name="time" placeholder="1000" ><br>
            <input type="text" name="id" value="43">

            <button type="submit">Upload</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>